__The Task:__
Perform a complete deletion of a temporary cache directory. Since some files might be locked or restricted, all error
messages must be silenced and hidden from the terminal."
__The Command:__
rm -Path '.\Temporary_Cache' -Recurse -Force 2> $null
__The Task:__
Create a new user account "Ahmed" for the Accounting department. The account must include a descriptive comment, mask 
the password during creation for privacy, and force the user to change their password upon the first login
__The Command:__
net user ahmed * /comment:"Accounting" /logonpasswordchg:yes /add
__The Task:__
Secure a sensitive directory "Salaries" on the C: drive. Disable inheritance to clear existing permissions, revoke all 
access for "Everyone", and grant "Full Control" exclusively to "Authenticated Users" while ensuring all future sub-items inherit these settings.
__The Command:__
mkdir C:\Salaries; icacls C:\Salaries /inheritance:d; icacls C:\Salaries /remove everyone; icacls C:\Salaries /grant "authenticated users:(oi)(ci)(f)"
__The Task:__
Offboard a resigned employee named "Mona" by immediately and permanently deleting her user account from the system to prevent any unauthorized remote or local access.
__The Command:__
net user mona /del
__The Task:__
Conduct a security audit to verify the members of the "Administrators" group, ensuring that only authorized users (and not unauthorized accounts like "Guest1") have elevated privileges.
__The Command:__
get-localgroupmember Administrators
__The Task:__
Configure a "Public_Docs" folder for collaboration. Grant "Everyone" the ability to read existing files and append new data/files, but restrict them from modifying or deleting any content created by others using specific NTFS flags.
__The Command:__
icacls C:\Public_Docs /grant "everyone:(oi)(ci)(rx,ad)"

























